multiFactorAuthenticationWarning.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPHttp] Message to show the end user when Multi Factor Authentication needs to be performed to access restricted information.
multiFactorAuthenticationWarning.value: Multi-factor authentication is required to show this page correctly.

disablePopUpBlockerWarning.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-SPHttp] Message to show the end user when pop up blocker is enabled on the current page.
